Nairobi County Majority Leader Abdi Guyo. [Edward Kiplimo, Standard]  Nairobi County majority leader Abdi Guyo lost four family members in a grisly road accident along the Isiolo-Nanyuki highway on Monday, March 28.  Isiolo County Commissioner Geoffrey Omoding confirmed that those involved were Guyo's brother, his sister-in-law and their two children.  The family was travelling to Isiolo from Nairobi when the accident happened.  Â  By Stephen Nzioka | 17 hours ago By Stephen Nzioka | 2 days ago By Nderitu Gichure | 5 days ago By Victor Nzuma | 7 days ago